text: Marta García Martín is a Spanish chess player, who achieved the FIDE International Master qualification in 2019. She currently belongs to the C.A. Mislata Lanjarón Discema team from Mislata, Valencia.Marta Garcia logra el titulo de gran maestra WGM García is the No. 3 ranked Spanish female player as of June 2019.Fide Ratings by Country. == References == == External links == * * *Marta García Martín chess games at 365Chess.com Category:2000 births Category:Spanish chess players Category:Living people Category:Chess International Masters Category:Chess woman grandmasters
